## ğŸ“‚ Project Architecture

Uses a straightforward **MVC (Model-View-Controller)** pattern suitable for media applications:

- **Model** â€“ Media data and playback logic
- **View** â€“ UI components (Buttons, TextViews, etc.)
- **Controller** â€“ Activity or ViewModel managing interaction

